pulfalight.title: Formatting of titles and dates is confusing
Remove separate date from the collection title

comments.body:
This is an indexing issue

The `parent_unittitles_ssm` method only appends the top-level (collection) title. `parents` in this method never have components:
https://github.com/pulibrary/pulfalight/blob/bc2427cdfb8b2da77561e3a4eeec77ea5509b395/lib/pulfalight/traject/ead2_component_config.rb#L109

The logic in this method and `parent_levels_ssm` does not work.

When I was digging into this I wasn't sure how to fix it with the new nested children indexing logic. Might have to adjust how the breadcrumbs are generated?

https://github.com/pulibrary/pulfalight/pull/222 was how we fixed it last time.
